Package trespass

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Trespasser<T>
    This marker interface must be extended by any interface used to define a dynamic proxy that can be created using the Factory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Factory
    Provides static factory methods to instantiate proxy objects according with properly annotated Trespasser interfaces.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidSignatureException
    Usually thrown when a proxy method signature is invalid.
    MissingAnnotationException
    Usually thrown when one of the annotations from package trespass.annotation was expected but missing.
